data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 3 bed, 4 bath condo with a full finished basement, patio, and deck. With tasteful finishes and abundant natural light, the main level boasts an open-concept living area flowing into a gourmet kitchen. A serene master suite and two additional bedrooms offer comfort and versatility. The fully finished basement provides endless entertainment possibilities. Outside, enjoy a charming patio and deck area. Conveniently located near amenities, this home offers modern living at its finest. New carpet in all of the bedrooms. Don't miss out - schedule your showing today!
